title: Anyone interested in starting a ranked 5s team?
body:
Hey guys,
I was wondering if anyone would like to join a semi-serious ranked team for just some fun, and to actually not stop after one game.
I am currently Silver 5 48 lp, and I am just over all the problems SoloQ has.
You would also have to be okay with me streaming our games (No one watches so don't worry haha)
